#: ../../talk/call.rst:3
msgid "Joining a call"
msgstr "Ag dul isteach i nglao"

#: ../../talk/call.rst:5
msgid ""
"When you're in a conversation, you can start a call any time with the "
"``Start call`` button. Other participants will get notified and can join the"
" call."
msgstr ""
"Agus tú i mbun comhrá, is féidir leat glao a thosú am ar bith leis an "
"gcnaipe ``Tosaigh glao``. Gheobhaidh rannpháirtithe eile fógra agus is "
"féidir leo páirt a ghlacadh sa ghlao."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:10
msgid ""
"If somebody else has started a call already, the button will change in a "
"green ``Join call`` button."
msgstr ""
"Má tá glao tosaithe ag duine eile cheana féin, athróidh an cnaipe go cnaipe "
"glas ``Glac páirt sa ghlao``."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:15
msgid ""
"During a call, you can mute your microphone and disable your video with the "
"buttons on the right side of the top bar, or using the shortcuts ``M`` to "
"mute audio and ``V`` to disable video. You can also use the space bar to "
"toggle mute. When you are muted, pressing space will unmute you so you can "
"speak until you let go of the space bar. If you are unmuted, pressing space "
"will mute you until you let go."
msgstr ""
"Le linn glao, is féidir leat do mhicreafón a mhúchadh agus do fhíseán a "
"dhíchumasú leis na cnaipí ar thaobh na láimhe deise den bharra uachtarach, "
"nó trí na haicearraí ``M`` a úsáid chun fuaim a mhúchadh agus ``V`` chun "
"físeán a dhíchumasú. Is féidir leat an spásbharra a úsáid freisin chun an "
"múchadh a athrú. Nuair atá tú múchta, má bhrúnn tú an spásbharra, dí-"
"mhúchfar thú ionas gur féidir leat labhairt go dtí go scaoilfidh tú an "
"spásbharra. Mura bhfuil tú múchta, má bhrúnn tú an spásbharra, múchfar thú "
"go dtí go scaoilfidh tú é."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:17
msgid ""
"You can hide your video (useful during a screen share) with the little arrow"
" just above the video stream. Bring it back with the little arrow again."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do fhíseán a cheilt (úsáideach le linn comhroinnt scáileáin) "
"leis an tsaighead bheag díreach os cionn an tsrutha físe. Tabhair ar ais é "
"leis an tsaighead bheag arís."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can access your settings and choose a different webcam, microphone and "
"other settings in the ``...`` menu in the top bar."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rochtain a fháil ar do shocruithe agus ceamara gréasáin, "
"micreafón agus socruithe eile a roghnú sa roghchlár ``...`` sa bharra "
"uachtarach."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:24
msgid ""
"From the media settings dialog, you can also change the background of your "
"video."
msgstr ""
"Ón dialóg socruithe meán, is féidir leat cúlra do fhíseáin a athrú freisin."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:29
msgid ""
"All these settings are also available as direct actions in the bottom bar."
msgstr ""
"Tá na socruithe seo go léir ar fáil mar ghníomhartha díreacha sa bharra bun "
"freisin."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:34
msgid "You can change other settings in the ``Talk settings`` dialog."
msgstr "Is féidir leat socruithe eile a athrú sa dialóg ``Socruithe cainte``."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:40
msgid "Download call participants list"
msgstr "Íoslódáil liosta rannpháirtithe glaonna"

#: ../../talk/call.rst:42
msgid ""
"You can download the list of participants in a call from the ``...`` menu in"
" the top bar. This will download a CSV file with the names and email "
"addresses of all participants in the call."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat liosta na rannpháirtithe i nglao a íoslódáil ón roghchlár "
"``...`` sa bharra uachtarach. Íoslódálfaidh sé seo comhad CSV ina bhfuil "
"ainmneacha agus seoltaí ríomhphoist na rannpháirtithe uile sa ghlao."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:47
msgid "The table in the CSV file contains the following columns:"
msgstr "Tá na colúin seo a leanas sa tábla sa chomhad CSV:"

#: ../../talk/call.rst:49
msgid "**Name**: The name of the participant."
msgstr "**Ainm**: Ainm an rannpháirtí."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:50
msgid "**Email**: The email address of the participant."
msgstr "**Ríomhphost**: Seoladh ríomhphoist an rannpháirtí."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:51
msgid ""
"**Type**: Indicates whether the participant is a registered user or a guest."
msgstr ""
"**Cineál**: Léiríonn sé seo an úsáideoir cláraithe nó aoi an rannpháirtí."

#: ../../talk/call.rst:52
msgid "**Identifier**: Unique identifier for the participant."
msgstr "**Aitheantóir**: Aitheantóir uathúil don rannpháirtí."
